## API

POST /offer
Content-Type: application/json
{
  "name": "AI Sales Assistant",
  "value_props": ["Automates lead qualification", "Improves sales efficiency"],
  "ideal_use_cases": ["B2B SaaS", "Sales teams with large lead lists"]
}

POST /leads/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data
File: leads.csv

GET /results




